rComments: I only have great things to say about Dr. Adnan. He is so passionate about teaching Islamic topics. He is so knowledgable, knows his stuff and is always eager to learn. I always leave his classroom learning something new. If i can do my bachelors again, i would only take his classes. God bless him !I wish more professors are like him! He's my idol!
Yes yes yes yes. Take all his classes he is amazing. So well spoken, such good insight.

Currently at SMU. Always enjoyed courses with Adnan. Fair marker, crystal clear and very understanding. Tries to make classes as interesting as possible and will always reward you for effort. Likes to engage with students and is very hip! Took two classes with him and got As in both I think. RELS 3370 and RELS-2323
